<p>1. Build and deploy:</p>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>git clone https://github.com/Deauthorized/python_openidconnect_starter_app</span></code></pre>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>cd python_openidconnect_starter_app</span></code></pre>
<h5># with pip</h5>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>pipenv install</span></code></pre>
<h5># with conda</h5>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>conda env create && source activate deauthorized-python-sample</span></code></pre>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>createdb python_getting_started</span></code></pre>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>python manage.py migrate</span></code></pre>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>python manage.py collectstatic</span></code></pre>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>heroku local </span></code></pre>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>heroku create</span></code></pre>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>git config --list | grep heroku</span></code></pre>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>git push heroku master</span></code></pre>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>heroku run python manage.py migrate</span></code></pre>
<pre class="prettyprint language-term"><code class="language-term"><span class="token input"><span class="token prompt">$ </span>heroku open</span></code></pre>
<br>

<p>2. Configure the OPENID_CLIENT_ID, OPENID_CLIENT_SECRET env for the starter app on Heroku. </p>

<p> OPENID_CLIENT_ID:
  <code>
                                                 <%= @app.openid_client_id %>
                                             </code>
</p>
<p> OPENID_CLIENT_SECRET: <code><%= @app.openid_client_secret %></code></p>
